data.description: Priced to Sale! Beautifully Remodeled, 3 BD-2 BTH home (SFR NOT MOBILE) that sits on a large 1.40 acre lot at the end of the road, with heated horse stalls (2), chicken coop, attached storage for hay and supplies, with horse arena. 2 other storage sheds, and unfinished separate unit approximately 900 sq ft (guest house, art studio, endless possibilities!), all fenced in with a gate open for your convenience. Surrounded by tall trees in the secluded Stoval Subdivision, only 14.5 miles to Bastrop TX, 21.6 miles to Tesla, Samsung and 32.2 miles to Austin Bergstrom Airport, in between the 290 & 95! No HOA!!
